<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The world we are living in is totally technology based. Human today cannot imagine the life without gadgets. Simple tasks to complex management systems are being designed by the technology. It is very important to stay updated in this contemporary world. Countries, who are not being able to do so our left behind. &nbsp;Especially the undeveloped countries that are lacking the resources and capital.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

